Title : Template:British pathe/doc
Text : {{Documentation subpage}}
{{info|1=This template is intended for [[Wikipedia:External links|external links]].  It is not designed for use as a [[Wikipedia:Citation templates|citation template]] for reliable sources.}}

<!-- Categories go at the bottom of this page and interwikis go in Wikidata. -->

== Usage ==
{{tlx|british pathe|''v''|''year''|''d''|''id''}}

=== Params ===
* {{param|v}} - Video identifier for the material at YouTube. (''Required'')
* {{param|year}}-  Year the mateiral is from.(''Required'')
* {{param|d}} - Description of the material, (defaults to Archive Footge) (''Optional'')
* {{param|id}} - Original id number for the material on the British Pathe website (''Optional'')

== See also ==
* {{tl|cite video}} - when citing audio and visual media sources this template should be used instead
* {{tl|YouTube}} - for linking to YouTube videos, when not citing, usually in [[Wikipedia:External links|external links]]
* [//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:LinkSearch&target=http%3A%2F%2F*.britishpathe.com&limit=500&offset=0 All wikipedia pages linked to BritishPathe.com]

